# Restructure Recommendations

## Summary

10 features → 7, plus a new `src/shared/` directory for cross-cutting concerns.
Eliminates most cross-feature import violations.

---

## Current Cross-Feature Import Map

| Feature                    | Imports From                                         |
|----------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
| keypad                     | (none)                                               |
| calorieEntryDisplay        | (none)                                               |
| additionalLoggingDetails   | (none)                                               |
| calories                   | (none — but owns the shared DB)                      |
| miniDailyDash              | calories, settings                                   |
| showLog                    | calories, appHeader, aboutPage (back.svg)            |
| settings                   | calories (dexieDb + clearTodayLog), aboutPage, showLog |
| appHeader                  | today                                                |
| aboutPage                  | appHeader                                            |
