## Future Considerations (out of scope for this restructure)

1. DUAL REPOSITORY CLEANUP — CalLogRepository (plain objects) and CaloriesLogRepository
   (domain-hydrated) overlap. Consolidate to one. Likely keep CalLogRepository and drop
   CaloriesLogRepository + the unused logCalorieEvent.js / getTodaysTotalCalories.js
   use-cases if they have no consumers.

2. SETTINGS AS ROUTING HUB — settingsOverlay.js directly imports createAboutPage and
   createShowLogPage, making it a de facto router. A future refactor could introduce a
   lightweight page-router in main.js to decouple navigation.

3. EMPTY SCAFFOLD FOLDERS — Remove .keep placeholder folders in miniDailyDash (domain/,
   infrastructure/, components/) since they have no planned content.
